NK106(me)002:1: // rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso'i 'grel pa

NK106(me)002:2177: bshad pas rtsal sbyong bogs kyi 'byin tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2178: gsum pa lhag mthong bsgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2181: bshad pas gsal dngas phyed lam yengs pa thabs kyi mchog tu bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2184: bshad pas dmigs rnams nges pa'i bsgom tshul bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2187: bshad pas rtsal sbyong bogs kyi 'byin tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2188: bzhi pa zung 'jug bsgrub pa'i thabs la lnga ste /
NK106(me)002:2191: bshad pas phyam gdal 'dzin med thabs kyi mchog tu bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2194: bshad pas dmigs rnams nges pa'i bsgom tshul bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2197: bshad pas gegs kyi dri ma sel thabs bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2200: bshad pas bogs 'byin gnad kyi man ngag bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2203: bshad pas rtsal sbyong zab don snying po bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2204: don gsum pa gang bsgrub pa'i ngo bo bstan pa la brgyad de /
NK106(me)002:2207: bshad pas brjod bral don gyi ngo bor bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2210: bshad pas sna tshogs du ma ro gcig tu bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2213: bshad pas 'char tshul ngang dngas skye med du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2216: bshad pas nyams rtags rol pa'i rtsal snang du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2219: bshad pas 'khor 'das rig pa'i rang snang du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2222: bshad pas chos rnams ye grol dbyer med du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2225: bshad pas snang sems sgyu ma gnyis med du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2228: bshad pas rig stong dbyings khyab gdal du bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2229: don gsum pa le'u rdzogs pa 'jug gi don la lnga ste /
NK106(me)002:2234: bcu gsum pa 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i le'u la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2237: le'u rdzogs pa mjug gi don no //
NK106(me)002:2243: zhi ba byang chub kyi brnyes tshul spyir bstan /
NK106(me)002:2244: sku lnga lhun grub kyi rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad /
NK106(me)002:2245: nang dbyings rnam dag gi 'char gzhis don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2249: bshad pas dag pa gnyis ldan gyi chos dbyings brnyes tshul dang /
NK106(me)002:2252: bshad pas zhi ba nang dbyings rtag tu mi g.yo bar bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2254: nang dbyings sku gsum gyi rang bzhin mdor bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2255: rang snang longs sku'i zhing khams rgyas par bshad pa /
NK106(me)002:2256: spyir snang sprul sku'i rab dbye rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2258: rnam dbye spyir bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2259: dbyings las gzhan du mi snang bar bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2263: bshad pas mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku /
NK106(me)002:2266: bshad pas mngon par byang chub sku /
NK106(me)002:2269: bshad pas zhi ba chos kyi sku bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2273: bshad pas nang dbyings mthar thug rgyal ba kho na'i spyod yul du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2276: bshad pas chos sku nyag gcig spros dang bral bas gzigs snang kun las 'das par bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2279: bshad pas gnas lugs rdzogs rim mthar thug bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2280: gnyis pa rang snang longs sku'i zhing khams bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2281: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i ngo bo mdor bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2282: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK106(me)002:2283: skabs don nges par don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2297: bshad pas zhing khams dang gzhal yas khang gi snang tshul /
NK106(me)002:2300: bshad pas rgyan dang bkod pa'i khyad par /
NK106(me)002:2303: bshad pas gdan khri'i rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2304: dus phun sum tshogs pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2308: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2312: chos phun sum tshogs pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2316: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)002:2322: bshad pas khro bo'i 'khor bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2323: gsum pa don bsdu ba la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)002:2326: bshad pas dkyil 'khor gzhan yang tshul 'dis dpag pa /
NK106(me)002:2329: bshad pas bde gshegs longs sku'i snang bar bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2332: bshad pas gdul bya rnams kyi snang yul min par bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2335: bshad pas dus gsum rgyal ba'i rang snang dag par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2336: gsum pa phyir snang sprul sku'i rab tu dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK106(me)002:2339: bshad pas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2346: 'dul byed ston pa'i rang bzhin spyir bstan /
NK106(me)002:2347: 'khor dus rigs lnga'i rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad /
NK106(me)002:2348: gnas skabs nges pa'i rang bzhin don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2352: bshad pas rten sku'i snang tshul dang /
NK106(me)002:2353: brten pa'i ye shes kyi gnas tshul lo //
NK106(me)002:2357: bshad pas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2362: bshad pas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK106(me)002:2365: bshad pas me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK106(me)002:2368: bshad pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK106(me)002:2371: bshad pas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK106(me)002:2374: bshad pas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK106(me)002:2375: gnyis pa 'khor dus rigs lnga'i rang bzhin la bdun te /
NK106(me)002:2378: bshad pas 'khor gyi sgrib pa sbyong tshul /
NK106(me)002:2381: bshad pas rtag tu gzhan don mdzad tshul /
NK106(me)002:2384: bshad pas rigs lngar 'thad pa'i rang bzhin /
NK106(me)002:2387: bshad pas de'i khyad par snang tshul /
NK106(me)002:2390: bshad pas phyed snang sprul sku'i nges tshig /
NK106(me)002:2393: bshad pas zhing khams de'i snang tshul /
NK106(me)002:2396: bshad pas mkha' spyod tshul 'dir bsdu tshul lo //
NK106(me)002:2397: gnyis pa 'gro 'dul sprul sku la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2398: 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2399: de la brten pa'i ye shes bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2400: de nyid nges pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2404: bshad pas thub pa drug gi rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2407: bshad pas re re'ang mtha' yas dpag med bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2410: bshad pas de'i rgyu mtshan 'bad pa dgod pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2411: gnyis pa de la brten pa'i ye shes la gnyis te /
NK106(me)002:2414: bshad pas ye shes kyi ngo bo bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2417: bshad pas ye shes gnyis kyi dbye ba bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2418: gsum pa de nyid nges pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2421: bshad pas ma dag gdul bya'i ston par bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2424: bshad pas 'gro sems mthun pa'i las snang du bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2427: bshad pas thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabs su bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2428: gsum pa sna tshogs sprul sku la gnyis te /
NK106(me)002:2431: bshad pas sprul sku'i snang tshul dang /
NK106(me)002:2434: bshad pas 'gro don mdzad tshul lo //
NK106(me)002:2435: don gsum pa nang dbyings rnam dag gi 'char gzhis don bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2439: gsum pa le'u rdzogs pa mjug gi don la lnga ste /
NK106(me)002:2444: spyi don gsum pa mthar phyin pa mjug gi don la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2447: bshad pas dge ba gzhan don du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2450: bshad pas brtsam pa'i 'thad pa dgod pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2453: bshad pas brtsam pa'i tshul brjod pas gzhan don du bstan bcos ji ltar brtsam pa'i tshul /
NK106(me)002:2456: phyi 'grel gyis rgyas par bshad pas bstan bcos bkra shis shing /
NK106(me)002:2457: 'phrin las rlabs che bar bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2458: 'grel pa rdzogs pa mjug gi don la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2459: bstan bcos brtsams pa'i gnas la basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2460: dge rtsa rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2461: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sbyar tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2463: brtsams pa'i bstan bcos kyi gnas la basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2464: rtsom mkhan gang zag gi yon tan basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2465: rtsom rkyen slob ma'i tshul basngagasa pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2467: thar gling snang byed kyi sgron mer basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2468: yon tan kun 'byung gi gnas su basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2469: skal bzang skye bo'i spyod yul du basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2470: mdo rgyud bstan bcos kyi blo mig tu basngagasa pa /
NK106(me)002:2471: byang chub lam bzang gi snying por basngagasa pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2472: gnyis pa rtsom mkhan gyi yon tan basngagasa pa la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)002:2473: zab cing rgya che ba'i gnas la sbyangs shing byang
NK106(me)002:2474: chub snying po'i lam la zhugs pas bstan bcos brtsams
NK106(me)002:2476: 'od gsal snying po'i de nyid rtogs shing skye med
NK106(me)002:2477: stong pa'i tshul la mkhas pas bstan bcos brtsams pa'i
NK106(me)002:2479: rang byung bla mas byin gyis brlabs shing dbugs chen
NK106(me)002:2480: 'byin pa'i lung bstan thob pas bstan bcos brtsams pa'i
NK106(me)002:2482: thugs rje'i byin rlabs rgyud la zhugs pas dngos 'dzin 'khrul pa'i ri bo bsnyil zhing /
NK106(me)002:2483: gzhan don 'phrin las 'od zer 'phro bas bstan bcos brtsams pa'i yon tan basngagasa pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2484: rtsom rkyen slob ma'i tshul la basngagasa pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2485: 'dod don bstan bcos kyi smon pa 'grub pa /
NK106(me)002:2486: skul byed gang zag gi rang bzhin bstan pa /
NK106(me)002:2487: grub ri rin chen gyi gnas la basngagasa pa'o //
NK106(me)002:2488: gnyis pa dge rtsa rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)002:2489: rlabs chen gzhan don du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2490: gnas skabs rang don du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2491: gnyis don dar rgyas su bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2493: thar gling byang chub tu bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2495: bde skyid phun tshogs su bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2496: dag pa'i zhing mchog tu bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2497: byams mgon zhabs drung du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2498: brtson 'grus dpe med du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2499: ded dpon mchog rab tu bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2500: srid 'gro bde chen du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2501: yang dag pa' mchog tu bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2502: gnyis pa rang don du bsngo ba la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)002:2503: tshe gangs nags su 'da' bar bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2504: mi rtog ting 'dzin 'grub par bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2505: 'od gsal snying po thob par bsngo ba /
NK106(me)002:2506: rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi med par bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2507: gsum pa gnyis don dar rgyas su bsngo ba la gnyis te /
NK106(me)002:2508: dge rtsa dar zhing rgyas par bsngo ba dang /
NK106(me)002:2509: bstan bcos dar zhing rgyas par bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)002:2510: don gsum pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i sbyar tshul bstan pa la lnga ste /
NK106(me)002:2516: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso'i 'grel pa
NK106(me)002:2517: shing rta chen po'i bsdus don gyi gnas rgya cher
NK106(me)002:2518: dbye ba / pad+ma dkar po'i phreng ba zhes bya
NK106(me)002:2519: ba mang du thos pa'i rnal 'byor pa dri med
NK106(me)002:2520: dbye ba / 'od zer gyis / gangs ri thod
NK106(me)002:2521: dkar gyi mgul me tog sprin gyi skyed mos tshal
NK106(me)002:2522: dbye ba / 'od zer gyis / gyi nang /
NK106(me)002:2523: kun du bzang po'i khang bzangs dam par thos pa
NK106(me)002:2524: dbye ba / 'od zer gyis / gyi nang / dang / bsam pa dang /
NK106(me)002:2525: sgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyis legs par sbyar ba rdzogs so //
